<plot>Extraordinary disabled artist Laura Ferguson creates three dimensional self-portraits using high tech inner-body scans and layered, textured paper. By exposing her insides, twisted by painful scoliosis, with breathtaking beauty and ingenuity, Laura makes us all marvel at the wonders we carry around inside us.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?321404</url></doc>
